    {
        "content": "<p>saulecabrera <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13856#issuecomment-4992933755\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13856\">issue #13856</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I am able to reproduce this one. Can you confirm that this one only fails on Aarch64 on your end? I was not able to reproduce on x86_64. If so, this is expected, since the Aarch64 backend does not offer support for [SIMD], yet. However, the error could be better here, I have opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13889\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13889</a> to improve the error message. </p>\n<p>[SIMD]: <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/9925\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/9925</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
